title: How to Paint: Battle Ready Seraphon Raptadon Hunter
description:
These skinks and their reptilian mounts swiftly close in on the foe, bombarding them with javelins and luring them to their doom. In this video, we’ll show you how to paint a Raptadon Hunter to Battle Ready.        

If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it
